E[X] = \sum_{x=0}^n x\binom{n}{x}p^x(1-p)^{n-x}=\sum_{x=1}^nn\binom{n-1}{x-1}p^x(1-p)^{n-x}
=np\sum_{x=1}^{n-1}\binom{n-1}{x-1}p^{x-1}(1-p)^{n-1-(x-1)}=np
